cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

The paper proposes a novel regularization method for training GANs, which is a popular topic in machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also includes theoretical analysis, which suggests that it may belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) or cs.GR (Graphics).
